Marinated jogre bones are a quest item that are made by cooking pasty jogre bones on a range. They are used in the Tai Bwo Wannai Trio quest. They can be buried for 17 Prayer experience each.

Image Examine Components Notes
Burnt Jogre bones marinated in a lovely Karambwanji sauce. Perfect. Burnt jogre bones and Raw Karambwanji paste Required
Jogre Bones marinated in Karambwanji sauce. Not quite right. Jogre bones and Raw Karambwanji paste Useless

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • If Marinated jogre bones are used with the bone grinder in the Ectofuntus of Port Phasmatys, a message will appear saying, "These bones could break the bone grinder. Perhaps I should find some different bones."
